name: Hogties
description:
Started messing with landscape images and didn't see this pose anywhere. I put an activation tag on an image set, trimmed some I didn't like, then trained it. Far from perfect, but if you're looking for hogties then this is somewhere to start! Naturally involves fingers and toes being in frame, so expect unreliability on that front.

Once again, highly recommend only using with bondage mixes involving: https://civitai.com/models/34777/bondage-v11 or its earlier versions. Otherwise, expect poor results.

Recommended weight: 1.0

Recommend using landscape orientation i.e. 768x512 / multiples of that
